        <updateDate>2022-03-07T19:33:42Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Blocking Appointees from Refusing Recusal Act or the BARR Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits high-level appointees in the Department of Justice from participating in particular matters in which the President, a relative of the President, or an individual associated with the campaign of the President is a party.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
